text: Well, the client stores the symmetric key the tx is encrypted with locally. The goal was ultimately to have a field in the tx where client also encrypts the tx key using its long term encryption key, so that it does not need to keep state.
Hello guys, maybe someone has faced such an issue? Thanks! <https://github.com/IBM-Blockchain/ibm-blockchain-issues/issues/45>
